name: Config Consultants
overview:
This axiom can be applied to the formation of the core team at Config Consultants. The Necessity of solutions to challenges faced by our clients combined with our drive and commitment to meet those challenges. After spending years on large projects for the Fortune 500 and Big 4 firms the managing partners at Config Consultants have come under one umbrella to provide end to end solutions for businesses of all sizes.

From the Garden City of Bangalore to the heart of the Midwest in Indianapolis, we have amassed a team of experts in both technical and functional knowledge that bring a wealth of “life” experience to the table. Simply put, we hire and retain people that we would like to have dinner with. Shared vision, respect and good old fashioned work ethic are the ties that bind.

We at Config Consultants stand ready to leverage our years of experience, technical expertise and best practices to overcome your business and technology obstacles. Contact us today, we are good listeners.
